com.googlecode.objectify.cmd

Interface QueryKeys<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<Key<T>>, QueryExecute<Key<T>>, com.google.appengine.api.datastore.QueryResultIterable<Key<T>>

    public interface QueryKeys<T>
extends QueryExecute<Key<T>>

    After you call Query.keys(), you are executing a keys-only query. This is the command structure. It offers only terminators; if you wanted additional filtering, add it before keys().
